\f1 \cf2 \expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Shawarma is a popular Middle Eastern dish featuring marinated meat cooked slowly on a spit and then shaved into thin slices. We've created a roasted version which is just as juicy and ready in a fraction of the time. The spiced chicken is served with warm naan, creamy tahini sauce, and a refreshing chopped salad.
