2 boneless skinless chicken breasts \
1 spice mix (1 teaspoon ground cumin \'bd teaspoon smoked paprika \'bc teaspoon turmeric)\
 
\f3 \uc0\u8539 
\f1  teaspoon cayenne pepper \
